\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b d}) Subsp. {\b verguinii} (Briq. & Cavillier) Dostál, {\i loc. cit.} (1976) ({\i C. procumbens} var. {\i verguinii} Briq. & Cavillier): Stems 20-30 cm. Upper leaves amplexicaul, greyish-green. Involucre ovoid-globose; appendages covering bracts.{\i  Alpes Maritimes}.
